Citation.sTitle: Solubility of Puerarin in Ethanol + Supercritical Carbon Dioxide
Citation.sAbstract: Equilibrium solubility of puerarin, a naturally occurring isoflavone C-glycoside, in the ethanol + supercritical carbon dioxide was measured at (308, 318, and 328) K and pressures up to 20 MPa. The results obtained are useful for the design of supercritical processes with this drug.
